<section class="sh-section">
  <div class="sh-container">
    <div class="sh-center"><div class="sh-eyebrow">Prepare. Optimize. Enhance.</div><h2 class="sh-h2">Three steps. One visible skin-refinement system.</h2><p class="sh-body" style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;">Each serum has a defined role. Together, they create a complete routine for skin that looks smoother, clearer, more even, and more refined.</p></div>
    <div class="sh-grid sh-grid-3" style="margin-top:42px;">
      <article class="sh-card step-card"><div class="step-number">Step 1</div><h3 class="sh-h3">Prepare Serum</h3><p class="role">The surface-preparation step.</p><p>Helps skin look fresher, smoother, and more ready for the next steps in the system.</p><p class="sh-small"><strong>Best for:</strong> rough-looking texture, dullness, lack of smoothness.</p><a class="sh-button sh-button--secondary" href="/products/step-1-prepare-serum">Learn Step 1</a></article>
      <article class="sh-card step-card"><div class="step-number">Step 2</div><h3 class="sh-h3">Optimize Serum</h3><p class="role">The core tone + texture step.</p><p>Designed to support the appearance of more even-looking tone, smoother-looking texture, and clearer-looking skin.</p><p class="sh-small"><strong>Best for:</strong> uneven-looking tone, dullness, visible pores, post-blemish mark appearance.</p><a class="sh-button sh-button--secondary" href="/products/step-2-optimize-serum">Learn Step 2</a></article>
      <article class="sh-card step-card"><div class="step-number">Step 3</div><h3 class="sh-h3">Enhance Serum</h3><p class="role">The tone + texture completion step.</p><p>Designed to enhance the final look of clarity, smoothness, polish, and refinement.</p><p class="sh-small"><strong>Best for:</strong> skin that needs a more finished, luminous, confident look.</p><a class="sh-button sh-button--secondary" href="/products/step-3-enhance-serum">Learn Step 3</a></article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
